snippet.title: Asleep Ato 1 - Official Trailer #AsleepAto1
snippet.description:
It's official, Asleep - Ato 1 still coming this year, AND we'll be announcing the launch date HERE, so stay tuned!

And don't forget to add the game to your wishlist and tell EVERYONE who would love to know about this news.

Available on Steam to Wishlist: https://bit.ly/AsleepSteam

Stay tuned at http://www.blackhole.games
Follow us on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/BlackHoleGames_
Follow us on Instagram:  https://instagram.com/blackholegames
